=========================
Installation instructions
=========================

1) System Requirements
----------------------

Operating system:
    Ubuntu 14.04
    NOTE: Other OSs such as Windows and OSX may also work with some work.


Simple Client:
    2GB of memory
    20GB of disk space
    2 CPU cores



2) Setup base OS
----------------

Install tools such as debuggers and memory analysis tools.

Update:
$ sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get dist-upgrade -y

Install required software packages:
$ sudo sudo apt-get install build-essential libc6-dbg git python3 python3-dev
  python3-setuptools psutils python-software-properties -y
$ sudo add-apt-repository ppa:ubuntu-toolchain-r/test && sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install libasan0
$ sudo easy_install3 psutil



3) Install Fuzzing Framework
----------------------------

Choose and install a fuzzing framework.

